review:
Best platformer which I have ever played and platformer is the first genre that I started to play video games when I was a very young (4yo) on SNES; 
Saying that I recommended this game would be too little for this game; 
I didn't have time to write the full review so this will be fine for now, will update it fully when I 100% it or when I get time for reviewing it;
Hollow knight helped me to heal up from deepest depression; 
I didn't experience a game like this for a long time, and I am very happy that this game will have future DLC and I can't wait for it also can't wait for future projects from developers (Team Cherry).
